            "title": "Naming",
            "id": 88828,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Similar a nombrar variables y funciones, hay algunas prácticas comunes al definir clases.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"class\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"Person\" class=\"title\" /><text value=\":\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  \" /><text value=\"def\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"__init__\" class=\"title\" /><text value=\"(self, name, age)\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\":\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"    self.name = name\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"    self.age = age\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"teacher = Person(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Emily&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"24\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\")\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"6\" endIndex=\"12\" /><option startIndex=\"98\" endIndex=\"104\" /></options></interaction></interactions></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Asegúrese de elegir <code>Person</code> seguido de <code>Person</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Class name",
            "id": 89046,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Los nombres de las clases generalmente tienen la primera letra en mayúscula y el resto en minúscula, como con <code>Person</code> aquí.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"class\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"Person\" class=\"title\" /><text value=\":\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  \" /><text value=\"def\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"__init__\" class=\"title\" /><text value=\"(self, name, age)\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\":\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"    self.name = name\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"    self.age = age\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"validatedInput\" isDefault=\"true\" startIndex=\"6\" endIndex=\"12\" /></interactions></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Asegúrese de elegir <code>Person</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Descriptive",
            "id": 88823,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Al igual que las variables, intentamos nombrar las clases de manera descriptiva.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"class\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"Book\" class=\"title\" /><text value=\":\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  \" /><text value=\"def\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"__init__\" class=\"title\" /><text value=\"(self, author, title)\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\":\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"    self.author = author\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"    self.title = title\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"0\" endIndex=\"5\" /><option startIndex=\"6\" endIndex=\"10\" /><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"B\" /></content></option></options></interaction></interactions></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Asegúrese de elegir <code>class</code> seguido de <code>Book</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Consistent",
            "id": 89048,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Al igual que con la nomenclatura de variables y funciones, debemos nombrar las cosas de manera consistente y prestar atención a la capitalización.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"class\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"Person\" class=\"title\" /><text value=\":\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  \" /><text value=\"def\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"__init__\" class=\"title\" /><text value=\"(self, name, age)\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\":\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"    self.name = name\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"    self.age = age\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  \" /><text value=\"def\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"sayHello\" class=\"title\" /><text value=\"(self)\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\":\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"    print(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Hello&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  \" /><text value=\"def\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"sayBye\" class=\"title\" /><text value=\"(self)\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\":\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"    print(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Bye&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"teacher = Person(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Emily&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"24\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"teacher.sayBye()\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"206\" endIndex=\"212\" /><option startIndex=\"212\" endIndex=\"213\" /><option startIndex=\"213\" endIndex=\"214\" /><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"Saybye\" /></content></option></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"Bye\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Asegúrese de elegir <code>sayBye</code> seguido de <code>(</code> y finalmente <code>)</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Other features",
            "id": 88771,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Al igual que los métodos fuera de las clases, puedes usar las funciones integradas de Python y sus características principales.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"class\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"Pie\" class=\"title\" /><text value=\":\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  \" /><text value=\"def\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"__init__\" class=\"title\" /><text value=\"(self, flavor, ingredients)\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\":\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"    self.flavor = flavor\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"    self.ingredients = ingredients\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  \" /><text value=\"def\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"print_ingredients\" class=\"title\" /><text value=\"(self)\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\":\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"    \" /><text value=\"for\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" i \" /><text value=\"in\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" self.ingredients:    \" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"      print(i)\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"applePie = Pie(\" /><text value=\"'apple'\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\", [\" /><text value=\"'flour'\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"'eggs'\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"'apples'\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"'butter'\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\"])\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"applePie.print_ingredients()\" /><text type=\"break\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"150\" endIndex=\"153\" /><option startIndex=\"154\" endIndex=\"155\" /><option startIndex=\"156\" endIndex=\"158\" /></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"flour\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"eggs\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"apples\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"butter\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Asegúrese de elegir <code>for</code> seguido de <code>i</code> y finalmente <code>in</code>.</p></body></html>"
